Other notable Shidori Shrines include:

* ''{{ill|Shidori Shrine (Tono)|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->'' (Tsuchibuchi-cho, {{ill|Tono, Iwate|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->, [[Iwate Prefecture]])
