* ''Shidori Shrine (倭文神社)'' in ''Shidori-go, Kume District, Mimasaka Province'' – {{ill|Shidori Shrine (Tsuyama)|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)--> (Yukikita, {{ill|Tsuyama, Okayama|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->, [[Okayama Prefecture]])
* ''Shidori Shrine (倭文神社)'' in ''Shidori-go, Mihara District, Awaji Province'' – {{ill|Shidori Shrine (Awaji)|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)--> (Shidori, {{ill|Minamiawaji, Hyogo|en}}
