Additionally, ''{{ill|Ōmika Shrine|8=ja|9=大甕神社|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->'' ({{ill|Hitachi, Ibaraki|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->, [[Ibaraki Prefecture]]) also enshrines ''Takahatsuchi-no-Mikoto|ja|天羽槌雄神|1=Takehazuchi|fr|Takehazuchi|zh|天羽槌雄神|lt=Takehazuchi-no-Mikoto''. Similarly, ''{{ill|Ishii Shrine|en}}
