<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->, [[Ibaraki Prefecture]]) also enshrines ''Takahatsuchi-no-Mikoto|ja|天羽槌雄神|1=Takehazuchi|fr|Takehazuchi|zh|天羽槌雄神|lt=Takehazuchi-no-Mikoto''. Similarly, ''{{ill|Ishii Shrine|en|12=draft}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->'' ({{ill|Kasama, Ibaraki|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Tottori)-->, [[Ibaraki Prefecture]]) enshrines the same deity, with a large sacred rock called "Mitarai" located to the south.
